      "description": "ProShares Trust - ProShares Ultra QQQ Equal Weight is an exchange traded fund launched and managed by ProShare Advisors LLC. The fund invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of global region. For its equity portion, the fund invests directly and through derivatives in stocks of companies operating across communication services, consumer discretionary, consumer staples, energy, health care, industrials, information technology, materials, real estate and utilities sectors. The fund uses derivatives such as swaps and futures to create its portfolio. It invests in growth and value stocks of large-cap companies. For its fixed income portion, the fund invests directly in U.S. Treasury securities. It seeks to track 2x the daily performance of the Nasdaq-100 Equal Weighted Index. ProShares Trust - ProShares Ultra QQQ Equal Weight is domiciled in the United States.",
